  "title": "Glossy Tangy Ethiopian Cranberries Misir Wot",
  "description": "A tangy and glassy Ethiopian dish featuring cranberries, cooked in a clay pot and suitable for a sick day, with ayurvedic tamasic friendly ingredients. This misir wot is a unique twist on traditional Ethiopian cuisine.",
