      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the clay pot over medium heat and add the oil.",
    "Add the chopped onions and saute until they are translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the berbere spice and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cranberries, water, and salt, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes, or until the cranberries have popped and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir occasionally to prevent burning.",
    "Serve the misir wot hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
